  "instructions": [
    "Pound garlic cloves in a mortar until well crushed.",
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add chopped red bell pepper and cook until tender.",
    "Add crushed garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add fideo noodles and stir to combine with garlic mixture.",
    "Add salt, black pepper, and paprika, and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for 5 minutes or until noodles are slightly toasted.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired."
